name: JsonPseudoList

values.name: jsonPseudoList
values.comment:
Read an object of the form

    >>> Json.Decode.decodeString
    ...     (jsonPseudoList Json.Decode.string)
    ...     """{
    ...           "length": 2,
    ...           "0": "hello"
    ...           "1": "world"
    ...         }"""
    ["hello", "world"]
